text: Włodzimierz Cimoszewicz (, born 13 September 1950) is a Polish politician. He was born in Warsaw, Poland. From 1996 to 1997, he was the 8th Prime Minister of Poland. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Poland Category:Marshals of the Sejm
title: Włodzimierz Cimoszewicz
